(? daily ops) Tj
T*
(? commercial ops) Tj
T*
(? sales, customer, and Shopify lanes) Tj
T*
(? queue-style operational follow-up) Tj
T*
T*
(### Desktop) Tj
T*
T*
(Use this for:) Tj
T*
T*
(? start runtime) Tj
T*
(? restart runtime) Tj
T*
(? stop runtime) Tj
T*
(? show window) Tj
T*
(? hide to tray) Tj
T*
(? prepare shutdown) Tj
T*
(? quit desktop app) Tj
T*
T*
(### System) Tj
T*
T*
(Use this for:) Tj
T*
T*
(? runtime readiness details) Tj
T*
(? speech and voice loop checks) Tj
T*
(? core agent checks) Tj
T*
(? startup health confirmation) Tj
T*
T*
T*
(5. VOICE WORKFLOW) Tj
T*
T*
T*
(JARVIS is designed for:) Tj
T*
T*
(? Norwegian and English input) Tj
T*
(? English reply output) Tj
T*
(? continuous voice loop support) Tj
T*
(? barge-in and interruption-aware behavior) Tj
T*
T*
(### If voice is not working) Tj
T*
T*
(Check these in order:) Tj
T*
T*
(1. Open `System`) Tj
T*
(2. Confirm speech backend is available) Tj
T*
(3. Confirm voice loop is active) Tj
T*
(4. If needed, use `Start Voice`) Tj
T*
(5. If the system feels stale, restart runtime from `Desktop`) Tj
T*
T*
(### Important safety rule) Tj
T*
T*
(Do not refactor or replace working voice behavior casually. Voice is one of the highest-) Tj
T*
(risk parts of the product and should be treated carefully.) Tj
T*
T*
T*
(6. DAILY USE PATTERN) Tj
T*
T*
T*
