T*
T*
T*
(JARVIS also supports operational business workflows such as:) Tj
T*
T*
(? sales intelligence) Tj
T*
(? customer interaction intelligence) Tj
T*
(? Shopify/store intelligence) Tj
T*
(? commercial ops missions) Tj
T*
T*
